block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: A request from you! This is an easy origami angel designed by Tadashi Mori, Angel 1.1. Tadashi Mori has his own channel too. Search him up. This marvelous angelic figure looks really cute. I had to make a video for it. Learn how to fold this awesome chibi angel in this video. I hope you like it. Enjoy!!! Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
